graph TD
    A[User Request + Artifacts] --> B[Diagnostic Agent]
    B --> C[Artifact Identification]
    C --> D{Artifact Type}
    
    D -->|Error Message| E[Pattern Match<br/>Known Errors]
    D -->|Stack Trace| F[Extract Exception<br/>Chain]
    D -->|Logs| G[Search Error<br/>Signals]
    D -->|Query Profile| H[Analyze Execution<br/>Metrics]
    D -->|Code| I[Static Analysis<br/>Anti-Patterns]
    
    E --> J[Confidence Assessment]
    F --> J
    G --> J
    H --> J
    I --> J
    
    J --> K{Confidence Level}
    K -->|≥80%<br/>High| L[complete<br/>DiagnosticReport]
    K -->|<80%<br/>ONLINE Mode| M[Context Enrichment]
    K -->|<80%<br/>OFFLINE Mode| N[request_user_input<br/>Specific Evidence]
    
    M --> O[get_spark_logs<br/>get_run_output<br/>get_cluster_events]
    O --> J
    
    N --> P[Wait for Evidence]
    P --> J
    
    L --> Q{Route to Specialist?}
    Q -->|Memory/Sizing| R[Cluster Agent]
    Q -->|Query Plan| S[Query Agent]
    Q -->|Job Config| T[Job Agent]
    Q -->|Permissions| U[UC Agent]
    Q -->|No| V[End]
    
    style B fill:#F5A623,color:#000
    style L fill:#7ED321,color:#000
    style K fill:#F5A623,color:#000

